Nearby regressions:
Bug: 298539299

Test: m com.android.btservices
Ignore-AOSP-First: security
(cherry picked from https://googleplex-android-review.googlesource.com/q/commit:ab986fe4165aae74c5915f57ad2e78bf80f1d3ec)
